ll inv(ll a, ll b){return 1<a ? b - inv(b%a,a)*b/a : 1;}
bb inv(bb a, bb b){return 1<a ? b - inv(b%a,a)*b/a : 1;}


bb CRT(const vector<ll> &a, const vector<ll> &n) {
  bb prod = 1;
  for (auto ni:n) prod*=ni;

  bb sm = 0;
  for (int i=0; i<n.size(); i++) {
    bb p = prod/n[i];
    sm += a[i]*inv(p, (bb)n[i])*p;
  }
  return sm % prod;
}







